name: Adults who smoke, Untied Kingdom, 2003-05
description: Association of Public Health Observatories publishes data on prevalence of adult smoking to estimate the prevalence of adult smokers. Smoking prevalence is a direct measure of health care need i.e. the ability to benefit from tobacco control interventions, including smoking cessation services.
